# Development Rules

## CSS/Design
- Follow mobile-first approach (styles apply to mobile devices by default)
- Use media queries for larger breakpoints
- Use flexbox for responsive layouts
- Do not use Grid layouts
- Always use position static as first choice for position property
- Static positioning is easy to manage and understand.

## Components
- Use NavBar component with NavBar.css for all pages
- Use button component with button.css for all pages

## Security
- Never commit sensitive information
- Use .gitignore to exclude sensitive files
- GitHub username: sonex-pro

## Project Structure
- fonts Roboto and Georgia
- Keep components modular and reusable
- Follow consistent naming conventions
- Document component props and usage
- All pages should have their own css file
